Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:06.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:12.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:19.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Jinnai Tomonori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has everyone heard of the phrase "set phrase"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:26.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So have you ever had the experience of being set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:32.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At a handshake event, a fan came over and said they were meeting me for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:36.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I said "nice to meet you" but was then told "it's not the first time we've met"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:39.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's bad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:40.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been trapped in a conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Those guys from Weekly Magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I was talking to them about something they already knew, so I confessed everything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After saying that, the guys actually looked surprised with a "is that so" look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how far the other side had investigated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, I had to give a press conference and get a divorce
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough from you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:58.18,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※In 2009, the day after he filed for divorce, he held a press conference and admitted that the reason for his divorce was that he was having an affair with multiple women
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:58.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't mention that, Junior, it was 10 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It happens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the theory I bring you this time is:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:10.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Is there anything you have to say to me?" If you're told this, you'll likely say something that's unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see  \N-That's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:16.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think we all think the same thing in that we'd definitely say something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this case, for example
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you go to Hamada's lounge and are told this line by Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll probably be interrogated for more than 2 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's if Hamada's getting told off by his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:28.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll confess until the sea runs dry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll just keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:33.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:38.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will they really say unnecessary things?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:39.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Connecting Udo's overuse of "Sorry" with Amano's daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will either notice the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:52.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And, if the pitcher and first baseman are magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:55.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can they use a hidden ball to get batters out one by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:20.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Is there anything you have to say to me?" If you're told this, you'll like something that's unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:25.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The initial pair is Impulse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy won't listen anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't really imagine what will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a little scary... truly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:37.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If he confesses to a crime or something, it's over for us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:42.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm quite nervous as the pranker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:49.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After calling out his partner under the pretext of "we need to discuss something," the verification begins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you haven't told me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So believable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:58.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So believable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something I haven't told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:03.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's something I haven't been told, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something that needs to be said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The autograph thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:18.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Autograph \N-Autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:29.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was requested to sign our autograph
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I signed your name as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it was requested...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:46.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not what i'm referring to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah...the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:50.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The gym
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:04:00.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I lost 2KG of weight after exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Had a slight change in body size
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, why would I call you out because of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:08.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You lost 7KG when you were forced out of the business because of the scandal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call you out today to talk about losing 2KG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I could say it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"It's like this" can also be said
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it's better to let you confess yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Western...Western restaurant thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what? What Western restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to open a western restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gotta get a health permit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems like the kind of thing that would actually happen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An interesting pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:41.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His look suits a Western restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Western food...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:47.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since i've been back at work I've wanted to open a Western restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has become an interrogation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although forced to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:55.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All he gives are useless updates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Explosive announcements seem to be few
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it about preparing to study abroad in summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:10.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to open a cooking channel on Youtube?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Debt...debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hair regrowth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dad...that I was beaten by my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The small material keeps on coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:29.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even telling a story like "I was beaten up by my father" is unbelievable for someone over 40 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally this guy is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After saying "it's not that" repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I say "It's this" then that's the end of it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I need to hear the words  \N-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't come directly from you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't be in the mood to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:53.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Things that I should say to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:59.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last thing he squeezes out after thinking incredibly hard is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What encounter? Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's see if it's right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Signed up for the dating app that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Laughing so obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really funny though
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never had the opportunity to find an attractive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this it? Eh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you register under your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it says "42-year-old company employee"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you upload photos?  \N-No, I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if you don't show your face, it's a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'll eventually end in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When we meet, it'll be "You're Teshita, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this something that will cause you problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, these kinds of things don't matter at all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we reveal the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These familiar faces will make you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After conveying the theory
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't air the thing about the dating app thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How are the results of the dating app
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:18.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The guy who "earns 150 thousand a year at the age of 42" has no chance at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A survey of seniors and juniors who usually have a good relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,TKO's Kinoshita-san seems pretty bad
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really stingy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Yukio's brain is a bit wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From what Matsushita says
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy keeps talking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're obviously trying hard but still being told they don't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why he doesn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We all work very hard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? What about Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:52.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nadal who does not stop badmouthing his seniors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will soon be faced with the statement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:04.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nadal, do you have something to say to me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it about LUMINE? LUMINE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Talking about your Heroshow segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Talking about our segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They've been doing the same thing for 18 years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"It's always the same, and the people listening to it remember it", something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think someone said that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anthony did
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anthony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Immediately betrayed the man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it really what Anthony said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"It's always Heroshow"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anthony? He was looking down on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Funny... funny damage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does funny damage mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand either
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:07.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've already heard about that, to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It reached my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't eat the mushrooms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finished it in one bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I told you not to eat mushrooms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really do not know what you are talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really do not want to be the one to say it, Nadal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...the private work thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to take private work, but I can barely afford to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:35.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How often do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not that often
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This golden week, there are "Golden Private Shows" and such
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can live well if you don't take private work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:46.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I hate to say this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:50.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,ZAKO said this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said "Why is private work dark?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said "Yeah"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:57.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He replied "When the darkness is gone, the light comes"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:57.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do private work, you're on TV after all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But its not this... private work does not matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,X？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not good not good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we disclose the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Always staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A good bad expression
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute Fujimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lot of good info came out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also said the X thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look at his eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What day of the week is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:56.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wed... Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't be like this, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,FUJIWARA's Heroshow segment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's being looked down on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By Anthony and you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No...that's what everyone says
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:11.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "everyone says so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:16.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is also a senior and junior who have a good relationship in private
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about the master-disciple relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently I heard some bad rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there something you're not telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:24.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bento? The bento thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bento...ah, bento...ah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I took the bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:40.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:41.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the lounge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You took my bento from the lounge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can it be this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I went with various people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have worked in various places with different people and done it there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bento thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've done it to loads of my seniors
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who? Your seniors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Viking's Nishimura and a few others
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who? Viking's Nishimura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this doesn't constitute a crime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything about crime in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:31.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But isn't this something that everyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the bento
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That? The thing with the AV actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Having dinner with the AV actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My wife realised
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:55.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kumomoto... I told her it was your fault
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:04.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And now my wife is wary of you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've overthinking it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:11.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As a liaison with an AV actress is exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:15.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kumomot's reputation is unexpectedly brought into question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this'll happen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And there's more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Macau?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?\N  -Macau?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Macau?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In Macau...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The thing about that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Woman from Macau?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was I there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You were there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We went together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't don't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no no
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:45.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With both about to suffer, the verification is brought to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Due to the damage it will bring to Kumomot's reputation, please cut this out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's reasonable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:02.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kumomoto's wife... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kumomoto's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:06.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:12.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last is Morita who will be questioning his junior
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:33.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last is Morita who will be questioning his junior
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You two have something to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what? What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'm leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if he's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's just us two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First? What do you mean, first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what? What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:15:01.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you have to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No there isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There must be something you have you say to me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:16.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't understand your reply at all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I already know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of interrogation is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not like that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not "not like that"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you know, then say it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it from your own mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am completely confused about what is going on here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.14,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere is getting interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you want to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:35.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I already know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you know then just say it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want you to hear it from your own mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing, I've said nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You just keep saying "I know, I know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:55.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unlike the previous three groups, this group does not have a particularly obvious senior-junior relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, the scene turns into an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have set up a personal office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:06.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is absolutely necessary to understand each other. It is not possible for us not to share things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:09.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since it's such an important thing, just say it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do you refuse to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:14.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Say it, or do you not know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you really want to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:16.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't just say "you know", it won't get the conversation going
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you hope to achieve with this type of set phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a "set phrase"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:29.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then just come with some evidence and say "what is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've gotta do both
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's because i'm not doing that that you don't want to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you confessed from the start I wouldn't be angry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What, is it a business thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Business?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, business? Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:17:00.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well... I took on jobs and so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:05.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I went alone and did a hosting gig
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:11.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell the company that I did it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He took the bait in the end in such a typical manner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:30.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The duo and their manager are the only three people in their company
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And thus engage in a private business-focused exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:38.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Morita, who couldn't hide his shakiness in the face of such a real betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not the same as ordinary private work
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because it's personal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? What? You took a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's also a bit related to this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think this is what you were referring to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not about this, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about the pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:59.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Basically just pocket money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to share half of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You take a share of all my solo work
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's because it's all on the firm's books, so it can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then isn't it wrong to do it outside of the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much did you take? Enough is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:14.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just say how much you've taken, and don't worry about the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much did you get paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,20？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You didn't talk about it with Yamane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't, so i'm sorry, but this is beside the point
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is obviously not what you wanted to ask about
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying this out loud means i've already half lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a loss
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is because of the way you are talking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A half-loss
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:41.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. \N -A half loss means you still have another half
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no no
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You just said half of it  \N-Wait, wait, wait, it's just one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not because there are two halves that you say "half lost"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something needs to be cut into two halves to have lost half of it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have something you need to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You also have something to say to me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:04.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, an unanticipated counterattack is launched
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:08.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like you said, it has to come out of your own mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This question is too annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, what about that? In Fukuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You took a job at the beginning of the year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:36.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At that time, we agreed to go to dinner with our clients
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only you said stuff like "I've got something later"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who didn't show up, saying "I'm going home"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I said, "I'm not feeling well, I'm going home."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bad health but you actually went out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:52.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You were in bad health but you went out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "huh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You went out at that time right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:02.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:03.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Don't go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You went out \N -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One of the girls sent me a private message
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, wait, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:13.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:14.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:15.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I already know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I got a private message from Fukuoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I work at a hostess club", like that, and you went there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This topic is closed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:30.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's weird you don't wanna talk about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, i'm tired
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that's tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really tired
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, we reveal the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What? What? What? What? What? What? Enough, i'm tired
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:43.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't get what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? You, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You did something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:56.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's strange for you to ask me "what's going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:58.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:06.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Due to the counterattack, Morita thinks that he has been counter-pranked
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A trick, right? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I knew nothing of it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:16.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of magic is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:23.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\c\3c}this a theory that no one benefits from
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very explosive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It became like an Obon Kobon event
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The way of quarrelling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved about Teshita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Each reveal was quite cute
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wants to run a Western restaurant and stuff like that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm cheering him on
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zun's Iio!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.07,0:21:59.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First time seeing you
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, I've been here two or three times already
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada, what has happened to him?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.89,0:22:07.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What theories have you brought so far?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.30,0:22:13.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 years ago, Udo's good nature is insane
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was particularly unusual about that verification
Dialogue: 2,0:22:18.94,0:22:21.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was Udo's various apologies
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.58,0:22:26.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was sorry for everything. \N -He apologized for everything
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.02,0:22:28.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry for almost hitting you"
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.24,0:22:30.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one even noticed  \N-Indeed
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last summer, I sat in front of the air conditioner
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Udo passed between me and the air conditioner
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.32,0:22:38.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then he turned around and said
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.05,0:22:44.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Sorry about blocking the cold air from the air conditioner for a moment, Iio"
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.22,0:22:48.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this regard, we have brought this project
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.91,0:22:52.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kyaeen's One-day Electric Linked Life
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.42,0:22:56.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One-day Electric Linked Life
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.15,0:22:58.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every time Udo says "sorry"
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.96,0:23:02.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Amano will receive a shock of electricity
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is pretty bad  \N-It's awful
Dialogue: 2,0:23:04.26,0:23:08.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The question is, can Amano solve the mystery?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.64,0:23:10.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And stop the shocks
Dialogue: 2,0:23:12.47,0:23:15.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Again, this is the type of project that benefits no one
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.11,0:23:20.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the one being shocked is Amano
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.07,0:23:23.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, the source of the current
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has been previously explored
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.29,0:23:26.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the issue
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.32,0:23:30.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, please take care of me
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Udo's mantra: "Sorry"
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.92,0:23:39.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At that time, to co-stars, staff and even agents
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He apologized like crazy and talked endlessly
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this schedule
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.47,0:23:52.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will Amano be able to detect the linkage and stop the current?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.92,0:23:56.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, at 10:00 a.m., it starts with
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.60,0:24:00.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Artiste Navigation Yeah!
Dialogue: 2,0:24:02.25,0:24:05.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using the Sunshine Shopping Building in Ikebukuro as a stage
Dialogue: 2,0:24:05.27,0:24:10.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Emotional Udo's trip begins!
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.07,0:24:12.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before you know it
Dialogue: 2,0:24:13.16,0:24:14.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you been to Sunshine City?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:14.47,0:24:16.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was just here not long ago
Dialogue: 2,0:24:16.53,0:24:19.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a planetarium.  \N-Oh, oh, planetarium
Dialogue: 2,0:24:19.33,0:24:21.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I remember, Amano he...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.84,0:24:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He worked as a planetarium narrator
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.00,0:24:30.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it was here in Ikebukuro Sunshine
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If not then {\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.35,0:24:32.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If not then{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&} sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.85,0:24:38.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It only takes 5 minutes and reaching the topic of Amano for him to say sorry for the first time
Dialogue: 2,0:24:39.16,0:24:43.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Amano, who is called out for a fake meeting
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.36,0:24:45.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will taste his first shot of electricity
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.46,0:24:52.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 1,0:24:51.41,0:24:52.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His meat is hanging out
Dialogue: 1,0:24:54.59,0:24:56.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A naughty peek at the belly
Dialogue: 2,0:24:55.71,0:24:57.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:00.18,0:25:01.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:01.48,0:25:03.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is scary...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:03.76,0:25:07.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Amano, confused by the sudden electric current
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.09,0:25:08.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is suddenly greeted by the program staff
Dialogue: 2,0:25:12.52,0:25:15.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:15.66,0:25:19.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 2,0:25:19.80,0:25:22.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts. Did you guys just do that?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:25:22.17,0:25:26.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What what what what what what, what a bunch of weirdos you are!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:26.10,0:25:28.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the...what the hell? What are you verifying?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:30.08,0:25:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Faced with an unaccustomed trick, it takes a while for Amano to get in the mood
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.92,0:25:38.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Subsequently, he is fitted with an electrical device
Dialogue: 2,0:25:38.49,0:25:39.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 2,0:25:39.85,0:25:42.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cute, so cute
Dialogue: 2,0:25:42.32,0:25:44.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry{\r}, can I ask you a personal question?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:45.79,0:25:48.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Idiot, idiot!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:49.63,0:25:50.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too... {\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}sorry,{\r} really
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.06,0:25:53.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts. It hurts a lot!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:53.41,0:25:55.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of experiment is this? Can't you tell me?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:56.53,0:26:00.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, it is impossible to reveal the details at this stage
Dialogue: 2,0:26:00.99,0:26:06.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead, we tell him to enjoy his day to the fullest
Dialogue: 2,0:26:06.48,0:26:09.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, some more meetings take place
Dialogue: 2,0:26:09.25,0:26:13.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the meetings...all have to be held in this state?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:14.79,0:26:24.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even though the meetings were fake, we carried on as usual
Dialogue: 2,0:26:24.33,0:26:27.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will be troublesome for others, its not good
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.56,0:26:34.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus begins Kyaeen's electric linked day
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.71,0:26:36.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once again
Dialogue: 2,0:26:37.17,0:26:39.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry, {\r}are there any special events today?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.21,0:26:42.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes yes yes
Dialogue: 2,0:26:42.75,0:26:44.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:26:46.12,0:26:46.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:26:48.52,0:26:50.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry,{\r} really,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&} sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:26:50.55,0:26:51.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry,{\r} taking up your time
Dialogue: 2,0:26:55.29,0:26:56.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, {\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}sorry{\r}
Dialogue: 2,0:26:59.23,0:27:00.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.24,0:27:02.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?  \N-I'm okay
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.93,0:27:08.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The conversation at the service desk alone involved 7 apologies
Dialogue: 2,0:27:08.67,0:27:10.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:11.34,0:27:13.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H14DFF8&\3c&H050510&}Sorry,{\r} what type of guy do you like?
